<!-- PAGE 1 -->
<div id="page_1" class="print-page" data-mercury="full">
	<hr><%= image_tag get_image_path, :alt => 'logo', :class => 'logo' %>
	<h2>CAMPAIGN CHAIR</h2>
	<p>The Campaign Chair works with the Pastor to lead, represent and promote the campaign. The Campaign Chair will moderate Leadership Team meetings, oversee and support assigned campaign teams, and speak publicly for the campaign.</p>

